ming from the CMB and matter\npower spectra it becomes an issue worth of further investigation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Mar 2005 21:03:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 14 Jul 2005 18:57:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2005 14:13:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-04-06"}
