es that the probability of a partner IMF production\nvia dynamical mechanism has a threshold (not present in the Ni+Al case) and\nincreases with the size of the target nucleus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Mar 2005 11:03:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-07-19"}
