ompletely determined by the Poincare stresses and hence the conventional\nrelativistic relationship between the energy and momentum is recovered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Mar 2005 16:01:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
